KSL.com’s new Uplifting Utah column showcases the good done by those around you.
Email us the social media post or a description of the story in 200 words or less to web@ksl.com with the subject line “Uplifting Utah” and we'll pick some to share.
— Barbara WrightTrucker To-Go Bags"When our family vacation was canceled for spring break due to coronavirus we decided to do a family spring break service project instead.
The kids collected donations for the past two weeks, and then spent spring break putting the kits together.
